item.title: Saint Philomena Prayers Episode 2
item.description: Welcome to the second episode of Saint Philomena Prayers. January 10th is the traditional birthday celebration of our little Saint. These podcasts serve as a promise made in announcement and propagation of the power of this little girl. Saint Philomena, Powerful with God, Pray for us! For more information about Saint Philomena please visit the Sanctuary web site. Sanctuary of Saint Philomena
